column10: A driver turning  left failed to yield at two pedestrians including a child in a stroller, crossing a crosswalk at an intersection. The pedestrian light was on. The driver not only failed to yield, but also honked several times at us to make us stop!!
Driver went full speed through a “hard” red light

Two cars turning left ran the orange or red arrow light, the pedestrian light was green, the two cars failed to yield to me with a red stroller and I was lucky I saw them and stopped to let them pass.
